IsoRealms is a modular, data-driven application framework and game engine.

Build Requirements (Linux dependencies):
 - cmake
 - libglew-dev
 - libsfml-dev
 - rapidjson-dev
 - liblua5.3-dev
 - libfreetype-dev
 - libcurl4-openssl-dev
 - libjson-c-dev
 - libssl-dev

Build Steps:
 - cmake -S . -B build
 - cmake --build build

Run Steps:
 - ./IsoRealms Projects/Spindizzy/Main.isorealms

Note: This project is in active development and APIs may change.
